just_use compare_engines.py

# label: TOOL
# role: measure how often beginner.py rescues a tricks-engine stall

For each random-dealt game, drive play with
`strategy.choose_play`. When the tricks engine stalls, run
`beginner.py` on the current state. Reports rescue rate
across N games.

Diagnostic — informs the corpus-construction filter
thresholds the hunt scripts use.
